description.en:
What is hiUNDEAD? 
hiUNDEAD is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of one mfers NFT in the Meta-Swap pool of Fracton Protocol. For each UNDEAD NFT added to the pool, the total supply of hiUNDEAD will increase by 1 million. In contrast, for each UNDEAD NFT redeemed from the pool, the total supply of hiUNDEAD will decrease by 1 million.
